day I'd find a way to kill you.

43:07.838 --> 43:10.508
Swear to fuckin' god
that's what he said to me.

43:12.342 --> 43:13.675
Creepy little fucker.

43:13.677 --> 43:15.446
I'll find a fuckin'
hole for him one day.

43:16.514 --> 43:19.751
Why would you son wanna
kill you, Mr. Zariakas?

43:20.583 --> 43:22.184
How the fuck would I know?

43:22.186 --> 43:25.854
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC)

43:25.856 --> 43:27.525
What the fuck is it
to you, Dill, huh?

43:28.293 --> 43:30.159
Maybe you can give me
the name of that street

43:30.161 --> 43:31.963
those little hot
red asses are on?

43:33.297 --> 43:35.429
Guy at the hotel said
there's only one cop in town

43:35.431 --> 43:36.664
