for the weekend

43:36.666 --> 43:38.967
so I can do whatever
the fuck I want.

43:38.969 --> 43:40.536
(CHUCKLING)

43:40.538 --> 43:42.474
(REEL CLICKING)

43:44.041 --> 43:46.877
Yeah, there's no law
on Plymouth right now.

43:48.445 --> 43:53.481
(DRAMATIC MUSIC)
(REEL CLICKING)

43:53.483 --> 43:55.483
Hey, give me that fuckin' rod!

43:55.485 --> 43:56.851
