- Come on.

43:56.853 --> 43:58.186
(SHOUTING)

43:58.188 --> 44:00.155
- Come on, get it in.
- No no no, it's just a shark.

44:00.157 --> 44:01.456
I don't give a fuck.

44:01.458 --> 44:03.224
- Give the rod to me.
- No I'm gonna cut him loose

44:03.226 --> 44:04.559
and let him ride.

44:04.561 --> 44:06.461
It's a shark, you
said you wanted tuna.

44:06.463 --> 44:07.530
Gimme the fuckin' rod,
come on, clip me in, come on.

44:07.532 --> 44:08.900
Duke, get the bucket.

44:10.134 --> 44:11.300
What are we looking at?

44:11.302 --> 44:13.369
450 pound great white,
enough to give you

44:13.371 --> 44:15.503
