44:20.577 --> 44:25.380
Whoa whoa whoa oh fuck!

44:25.382 --> 44:28.184
Whoa, whoa, hey,
Gimme a hand, man!

44:28.186 --> 44:29.086
Jesus Christ!

44:36.927 --> 44:39.730
(MOTOR RUMBLING)

44:49.773 --> 44:52.210
(TENSE MUSIC)

45:04.255 --> 45:05.253
(LAUGHING)

45:05.255 --> 45:06.387
Hey baby!

45:06.389 --> 45:07.458
You see what Daddy caught?

45:07.925 --> 45:09.124
Big fuckin' shark.

45:09.126 --> 45:12.927
Honey I swear tomorrow I'm
gonna get you a big fat tuna.

45:12.929 --> 45:14.798
Or some fuckin' heads
are gonna roll.

45:15.532 --> 45:17.202
